description:
Lee is the brother of Mike Allred and noted author of alternate history novels.

He has worked on Solo #7 and Madman Atomic Comics #8. He took over writing duties on Marvel's FF from Matt Fraction while his brother Mike continued on art. The final arc (where the Future Foundation fought Doctor Doom was all penned by Lee.

Mike says of his brother, "he is one of the smartest people I know."
name: Lee Allred
